title: Hour 2: What Do You Have On Oddibe McDowell?
description:
Mike Schur joins to discuss the breaking news of Blake Bortles retirement. He also gets to Late Night TV, Tom Brady, Tua, and his Stat of the Day. Then, a University of Utah student is going nuclear and Elon Musk interviews Papi.
